<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Fake PDF</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Quarterly Report</h1>
  <p>This file is actually HTML saved with a .pdf extension.</p>
  <p>There is no %PDF header, no PDF objects, and no xref table.</p>
  <p>If a validator inspects the raw content, it should flag this as suspicious.</p>
</body>
</html>
